For a **Next.js 15 + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui** project, here's a production-ready `.gitignore`:

```gitignore
# ============================================
# Dependencies
# ============================================
node_modules/

# ============================================
# Next.js
# ============================================
.next/
out/
build/

# ============================================
# Production
# ============================================
dist/

# ============================================
# Logs
# ============================================
logs/
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# ============================================
# Environment Variables
# ============================================
.env
.env.local
.env.development.local
.env.production.local
.env.test.local
.env*.local

# ============================================
# TypeScript
# ============================================
*.tsbuildinfo
next-env.d.ts

# ============================================
# IDEs & Editors
# ============================================
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# ============================================
# macOS
# ============================================
.DS_Store

# ============================================
# Windows
# ============================================
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# ============================================
# Coverage
# ============================================
coverage/
.nyc_output/

# ============================================
# Testing
# ============================================
playwright-report/
test-results/

# ============================================
# Cache
# ============================================
.cache/
.parcel-cache/
.turbo/
.eslintcache

# ============================================
# Package Managers
# ============================================
.pnpm-store/
.npm/

# Yarn
.yarn/*
!.yarn/releases
!.yarn/plugins
!.yarn/sdks
!.yarn/versions

# ============================================
# Temporary Files
# ============================================
tmp/
temp/

# ============================================
# Vercel
# ============================================
.vercel/

# ============================================
# Firebase
# ============================================
.firebase/

# ============================================
# Docker
# ============================================
docker-compose.override.yml

# ============================================
# Miscellaneous
# ============================================
*.pem
*.key
*.crt
```


